title: Increased mTOR signaling, impaired autophagic flux and cell-to-cell viral transmission are hallmarks of SARS-CoV-2 infection
The adenosine analogue prodrug ATV006 is orally bioavailable and has potent preclinical efficacy against SARS-CoV-2 and its variants
Public T-cell epitopes shared among SARS-CoV-2 variants are presented on prevalent HLA class I alleles
